==Mandarin==

===Pronunciation===
[[Pinyin]]: xìa bĭ rú yŏu shén

===Phrase===
'''[[下笔]][[如]][[有]][[神]]''' ([[Simplified Chinese]])

# (''idiom'') To write as if by divine inspiration.

#: ''[[读书破万卷]]，'''下笔如有神'''.'' ([[Simplified Chinese]])

#: ''[[读书破万卷|讀書破萬卷]]，'''下筆如有神'''.'' ([[Traditional Chinese]])

===Alternate forms===
[[下筆]][[如]][[有]][[神]] ([[Traditional Chinese]])


===Related terms===
[[下笔如神]] ([[Simplified Chinese]])

[[下笔如神|下筆如神]] ([[Traditional Chinese]])

